snippet.title: Resident Evil: The Missions - Gameplay [Java Game]
snippet.description:
Resident Evil: The Missions it was a java game developed by CAPCOM Mobile and released in 2007

Play 50 entirely new zombie-hunting missions in this mobile update to the survival horror series. You play as one of the last remaining survivors of the elite S.T.A.R.S. police unit. Armed with a few weapons and a dwindling supply of ammo you must fight your way through a crumbling mansion overrun with monsters and horrific preternatural mutations.

Link to the game: http://dedomil.net/games/2709/screen/8
Version used in video - K850i 

Please like and subscribe to my channel if you liked this video, this way you motivate me to keep making new videos for you.
